title: Couchbase Nodes: Size of Views
agents: special
catalog: app/couchbase
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This service monitors the size of couch views on a cluster node.
 The space on disk as well as the actual data size is reported.
 Levels can be defined using the WATO rule "Couchbase Node: Size of couch views".

inventory:
 One service is created for each node.

item:
 The name of the node.
